entry.title: Israel Says It Found Evidence of Hamas Activity at Gaza Hospital
entry.content: Israel released footage that it said proved the Al-Shifa Hospital compound was being used by Hamas militants, in an episode that carries high stakes for both sides of the war.

entry.title: FDIC Chair, Known for Temper, Ignored Bad Behavior in Workplace
entry.content: Martin Gruenberg set a tone that left alleged harassment and discrimination unpunished at the bank regulator. After a WSJ investigation, he came under scrutiny at congressional hearings.
